I have enabled entropy annealing by default currently, but will add parameters to control it later. For now the parameter values are initial_entropy=0.3, min_entropy=0.005, cycle_length=35_000, damping_factor=0.5, do_entropy_annealing=True. We will go for 40_000 steps_per_env and same seed as run 22. Hopefully we reach the minimum bic score.
